<section class="hero hero--mono">
  <div class="hero-lines" aria-hidden="true" data-parallax="slow"></div>
  <div class="container hero-grid">
    <div class="hero-copy reveal" data-reveal>
      <p class="eyebrow">Mortgage brokerage</p>
      <h1 class="display">Financing with discipline and a steady path to closing</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        <strong>Sood Mortgages Group</strong> helps homebuyers and homeowners compare loan structures with confidence — clear documentation expectations, lender-neutral guidance, and communication you can forward to your CPA or attorney without second-guessing.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="btn btn--primary" href="/contact">Schedule a consultation</a>
        <a class="btn btn--ghost" href="/services">View loan programs</a>
      </div>
      <dl class="hero-stats">
        <div>
          <dt>Focus</dt>
          <dd>Purchase &amp; refi</dd>
        </div>
        <div>
          <dt>Approach</dt>
          <dd>Documentation-first</dd>
        </div>
        <div>
          <dt>Industry</dt>
          <dd>Mortgage broker</dd>
        </div>
      </dl>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-aside-stack">
      <figure class="media-frame media-frame--hero reveal" data-reveal style="--delay: 40ms" data-parallax="subtle">
        <img
          src="<%= images.homeHero %>"
          alt="Modern home exterior — representing purchase and refinance clients we serve"
          width="1400"
          height="933"
          loading="eager"
          decoding="async"
          fetchpriority="high"
        />
        <figcaption class="media-caption">Residential financing — structured for clarity from first call to keys.</figcaption>
      </figure>
      <aside class="hero-panel card reveal" data-reveal style="--delay: 80ms">
        <p class="panel-kicker">Why clients choose us</p>
        <h2 class="h3">Corporate clarity, not sales pressure</h2>
        <ul class="checklist">
          <li>Side-by-side scenarios for rate, term, and cash-to-close — in plain language.</li>
          <li>Underwriting readiness: we flag gaps early so you are not surprised at the eleventh hour.</li>
          <li>Coordination with your real estate agent and title partner when timelines tighten.</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="text-link" href="/about">Meet the brokerage →</a>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container split split--media">
    <div class="split-copy reveal" data-reveal>
      <h2 class="section-title">Built for the mortgage process as it exists today</h2>
      <p class="muted">
        The <strong>Mortgage Broker</strong> channel exists to widen your options while keeping a single point of accountability. We prioritize compliant disclosure, realistic timelines, and a file that stands up to investor guidelines — because a smooth closing protects your deposit and your peace of mind.
      </p>
    </div>
    <figure class="media-frame media-frame--tall split-image reveal" data-reveal style="--delay: 50ms" data-parallax="subtle">
      <img
        src="<%= images.homeProcess %>"
        alt="Desk with documents and laptop — documentation-first mortgage advisory"
        width="1200"
        height="900"
        loading="lazy"
        decoding="async"
      />
    </figure>
    <div class="card card--accent split-quote reveal" data-reveal style="--delay: 60ms">
      <p class="pull-quote">“We treat every application like it will be audited tomorrow — because disciplined files close on time.”</p>
      <p class="muted small">— Sood Mortgages Group advisory standard</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--band">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head reveal" data-reveal>
      <h2 class="section-title">Loan types we structure every week</h2>
      <p class="muted narrow-inline">Corporate-grade file prep across common channels — so your story matches what agency and investor guidelines expect.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="program-grid">
      <article class="program-tile card reveal" data-reveal>
        <h3 class="h3">Conventional</h3>
        <p class="muted small">Fixed and ARM, primary and second homes, conforming and high-balance when the property and borrower profile fit.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="program-tile card reveal" data-reveal style="--delay: 40ms">
        <h3 class="h3">FHA</h3>
        <p class="muted small">Lower down payment paths with clear mortgage insurance mechanics explained before you write an offer.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="program-tile card reveal" data-reveal style="--delay: 80ms">
        <h3 class="h3">VA</h3>
        <p class="muted small">Eligibility, funding fee, and residual income — organized for lenders that specialize in military and veteran files.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="program-tile card reveal" data-reveal style="--delay: 120ms">
        <h3 class="h3">USDA</h3>
        <p class="muted small">Rural and suburban eligibility maps, income caps, and guarantee fee impacts modeled in your disclosures.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="program-tile card reveal" data-reveal style="--delay: 40ms">
        <h3 class="h3">Jumbo &amp; non-conforming</h3>
        <p class="muted small">Reserve, asset depletion, and investor overlays communicated early — fewer surprises after submission.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="program-tile card reveal" data-reveal style="--delay: 80ms">
        <h3 class="h3">Investor &amp; DSCR</h3>
        <p class="muted small">Rental income documentation and leverage limits framed against your long-term real estate strategy.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container split split--flip">
    <figure class="media-frame reveal" data-reveal data-parallax="subtle">
      <img
        src="<%= images.homeLender %>"
        alt="Professional reviewing mortgage documents with a client"
        width="900"
        height="600"
        loading="lazy"
        decoding="async"
      />
    </figure>
    <div class="reveal" data-reveal style="--delay: 60ms">
      <p class="eyebrow">Purchase &amp; refi</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Built for competitive housing markets</h2>
      <p class="muted">
        When inventory moves fast, sellers and listing agents notice <strong>clean pre-approvals</strong> and responsive loan partners. We align your letter, your price point, and your timeline — and we stay available when the inspection clock is ticking.
      </p>
      <ul class="checklist">
        <li>Offer-stage guidance on financing contingencies and appraisal gaps.</li>
        <li>Refinance checkpoints: break-even, tax questions (with your CPA), and cash-out discipline.</li>
        <li>Investment property debt coverage and reserve modeling in plain numbers.</li>
      </ul>
      <a class="text-link" href="/services">Explore programs in detail →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--dark">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head reveal" data-reveal>
      <h2 class="section-title">How we work with you</h2>
      <p class="muted narrow-inline">Three stages with defined outputs — so you always know what we need next and why it matters.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="steps steps--with-image">
      <figure class="media-frame media-frame--steps reveal" data-reveal data-parallax="subtle">
        <img
          src="<%= images.homeClosing %>"
          alt="Hands exchanging keys — milestone of a successful home closing"
          width="1000"
          height="667"
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
        />
      </figure>
      <article class="step-card reveal" data-reveal style="--delay: 40ms">
        <span class="step-index">01</span>
        <h3>Qualify &amp; structure</h3>
        <p class="muted">Goals, income documentation, credit profile, and property type — aligned before we request lender disclosures.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="step-card reveal" data-reveal style="--delay: 50ms">
        <span class="step-index">02</span>
        <h3>Compare &amp; lock</h3>
        <p class="muted">Program fit, pricing trade-offs, and lock strategy — with written summaries you can revisit with family or advisors.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="step-card reveal" data-reveal style="--delay: 100ms">
        <span class="step-index">03</span>
        <h3>Close with confidence</h3>
        <p class="muted">Processor updates, appraisal and title milestones, and a final review of closing figures before you sign.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container split split--flip split--flip-reverse">
    <div class="reveal" data-reveal>
      <p class="eyebrow">Your team on the transaction</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">We speak the same language as your agent and title partner</h2>
      <p class="muted">
        A marketable closing is a coordinated closing. We provide milestone updates your real estate professional can drop into the file, and we flag underwriting conditions that affect <strong>CD timing</strong> before you are sitting at the signing table.
      </p>
      <div class="pill-row" aria-label="Partners we coordinate with">
        <span class="pill">Listing &amp; buyer agents</span>
        <span class="pill">Title &amp; escrow</span>
        <span class="pill">Insurance agents</span>
        <span class="pill">CPAs &amp; attorneys</span>
        <span class="pill">Builders</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <figure class="media-frame reveal" data-reveal style="--delay: 50ms" data-parallax="subtle">
      <img
        src="<%= images.homeFamily %>"
        alt="Family in a home — representing homeowners and buyers we guide through financing"
        width="1000"
        height="667"
        loading="lazy"
        decoding="async"
      />
    </figure>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--muted">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head reveal" data-reveal>
      <h2 class="section-title">What clients say about working with us</h2>
      <p class="muted narrow-inline">Representative feedback — names withheld for privacy; every file is different.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="testimonial-grid">
      <blockquote class="testimonial card reveal" data-reveal>
        <p class="testimonial-quote">“We received a comparison sheet before we ever picked a lender. No hype — just numbers we could take to our CPA.”</p>
        <footer class="testimonial-meta"><span class="testimonial-role">Refinance client</span></footer>
      </blockquote>
      <blockquote class="testimonial card reveal" data-reveal style="--delay: 50ms">
        <p class="testimonial-quote">“Our agent said the pre-approval read like someone had actually looked at our tax returns. That mattered in a multiple-offer situation.”</p>
        <footer class="testimonial-meta"><span class="testimonial-role">First-time buyer</span></footer>
      </blockquote>
      <blockquote class="testimonial card reveal" data-reveal style="--delay: 100ms">
        <p class="testimonial-quote">“Self-employed documentation was organized by year and trend. Conditions came back without the usual back-and-forth.”</p>
        <footer class="testimonial-meta"><span class="testimonial-role">Business owner</span></footer>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--dark">
  <div class="container narrow prose-block reveal" data-reveal>
    <h2 class="section-title">Licensing &amp; disclosures</h2>
    <p class="muted">
      <strong>Sood Mortgages Group</strong> is presented here as a mortgage brokerage for demonstration purposes. Rates, fees, and program availability change with markets and investor guidelines. Your loan officer will provide state-specific licensing identifiers and regulatory disclosures required for your transaction.
    </p>
    <p class="muted">
      This website is educational and marketing content — not a credit decision, rate lock, or commitment to lend.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container cta-band reveal" data-reveal>
    <div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Ready for a structured conversation?</h2>
      <p class="muted">Tell us whether you are buying, refinancing, or exploring options — we reply with next steps and a short list of documents to gather.</p>
    </div>
    <a class="btn btn--primary" href="/contact">Contact Sood Mortgages Group</a>
  </div>
</section>
